tt company inc and link flight simulation in the  also singer bought out gps systems and added it to the link simulations systems division lssd this unit produced nuclear power plant control center simulators in silver spring md while flight simulators were produced in binghamton new york in  corporate raider paul bilzerian made a greenmail run at singer and ended up owning the company when no white knight rescuer appeared to recover his money bilzerian sold off parts of the company kearfott was split the kearfott guidance  navigation corporation was sold to the astronautics corporation of america in  and the electronic systems division was purchased by gecmarconi in  renamed gecmarconi electronic systems and later incorporated into bae systems the four link divisions developing and supporting industrial and flight simulation were sold to canadian avionics engineering cae and became caelink the sewing machine division was sold in  to semitech microelectronics a publicly traded torontobased company for several years in the s singer set up a national sales force for cat phototypesetting machines of unix troff fame made by another massachusetts company graphic systems inc this division was purchased by wang laboratories in  st centuryedit woman with singer sewing machine in east timor  the singer corporation produces a range of consumer products including electronic sewing machines it is now part of svp worldwide which also owns the pfaff and husqvarna viking brands which is in turn owned by kohlberg  company which bought singer in  its main competitors are brother industries janome aisin seiki—a toyota group company that manufactures toyota necchi and er classic sewing machines and juki singer buildingsedit singer was heavily involved in manhattan real estate in the s through edward clark a founder of the company clark had built the dakota apartments and other manhattan buildings in the s in  the singer company retained ernest flagg to build a story loft building at broadway and prince street in lower manhattan the building is now considered architecturally notable and has been restored the story singer building completed in  was also designed by flagg who designed two landmark residences for bourne constructed during bournes tenure the singer building demolished in  was then the tallest building in the world and was the tallest building to be intentionally demolished until the twin towers of the world trade center were destroyed in the september  attacks at their clydebank scotland factory singer built a  ft clock tower which stood over the central wing and had the reputation of being the largest fourfaced clock in the world each face weighed five tons and it took four men fifteen minutes twice a week to keep it wound singer railway station built to serve the factory is still in existence to this day the famous singer house designed by architect pavel suzor was built in – at nevsky prospekt in saint petersburg for headquarters of the russian branch of the company this modern style building situated just opposite to the kazan cathedral is officially recognized as an object of russian historicalcultural heritage list of company presidentsedit isaac singer – inslee hopper – edward c clark – george ross mckenzie – frederick gilbert bourne – sir douglas alexander – milton c lightner – donald p kircher – joseph bernard flavin – paul bilzerian – iftikhar ahmed – stephen h goodman – four best selling domestic singer sewing machinesedit a singer model k fiddlebed from  a singer user book in france  a singer model  with lotus decals from  a singer model  from  a singer featherweight model k from  see alsoedit history of the sewing machine aisin seiki singer railway station toyota sewing machines patent pool referencesedit  cunningham john t  ellis island immigrations shining center arcadia publishing isbn    sewing machine history  sewing machines machinehistorycom retrieved    fort moultrie centennial part ii charleston walker evans  co